Package com.example.fairdraw.Models

Class Entrant

java.lang.Object
com.example.fairdraw.Models.Entrant
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Entrant extends Object implements Serializable
Model representing an entrant in the application. An Entrant holds entrant-specific data such as event participation history, notification preferences and a list of notifications. It is linked to a User via the deviceId field.
